Introduction

X:IN is a five-member multinational girl group under Escrow Entertainment. They made their official debut on April 11, 2023 with the single "Keeping the Fire".

Before the group's official debut, they released a single album "Who Am I" in March 2023.

On June 8, 2023, it was announced that member Chi.U would be leaving the group due to personal circumstances.

On July 8, 2023, it was announced that Roa would leave the group and two new members Hannah and Nizz were added to the group.
